  “Summer is officially here…” the singer captioned the glamorous photographs. Nicole posed for some selfies with Thom and fashion designer Julien MacDonald as they enjoyed their time on a boat in Ibiza. Nicole wore a busty blue patterned bikini top, which highlighted her incredible figure. She covered her bottom half with a turquoise wrap with a contrasting pattern. Nicole wore her long, dark hair back as she accessorised with earrings and some shades.   